<html>
<head>
<title>Student Feedback Form</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>🎓 Student Feedback Form</h1>
<p>Please fill all fields carefully.</p>
<form>
<h3>Student Details</h3>
<label>Name:</label><br>
<input type="text" required><br><br>
<label>Email:</label><br>
<input type="email" required><br><br>
<label>Course:</label><br>
<input type="text" required><br><br>
<label>Semester:</label><br>
<input type="number" min="1" max="8" required><br><br>
<hr>
<h3>ICLA Feedback</h3>
<label>How was the subject?</label><br>
<input type="radio" name="s1" required> Excellent
<input type="radio" name="s1"> Good
<input type="radio" name="s1"> Average
<input type="radio" name="s1"> Poor
<br><br>
<label>Difficulty Level:</label><br>
<input type="radio" name="s1d" required> Easy
<input type="radio" name="s1d"> Medium
<input type="radio" name="s1d"> Hard
<br><br>
<label>Rate (1–10):</label><br>
<input type="range" min="1" max="10" required>
<br><br>
<label>Comments:</label><br>
<textarea rows="3" cols="40" required></textarea>
<hr>
<h3>SMP Feedback</h3>
<label>How was the subject?</label><br>
<input type="radio" name="s2" required> Excellent
<input type="radio" name="s2"> Good
<input type="radio" name="s2"> Average
<input type="radio" name="s2"> Poor
<br><br>
<label>Difficulty Level:</label><br>
<input type="radio" name="s2d" required> Easy
<input type="radio" name="s2d"> Medium
<input type="radio" name="s2d"> Hard
<br><br>
<label>Rate (1–10):</label><br>
<input type="range" min="1" max="10" required>
<br><br>
<label>Comments:</label><br>
<textarea rows="3" cols="40" required></textarea>
<hr>
<input type="submit" value="Submit">
</form>
</body>
</html>
